{"tid":890917,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"西遊記2 仙履奇緣 有野睇唔明","createTime":"2018-11-05T16:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T16:59:24.000Z","uid":71704,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f345a0ba7d75a574f4fde90244310883d36505d","tid":890917,"uid":71704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"點解師父臨尾同一開頭性格完全唔同左？"},{"pid":"ee8720dfff382aec8787a498e1cd4078b2471454","tid":890917,"uid":71704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a15a3054f9d771a7d332fba294adf0b8aaaa175","tid":890917,"uid":203357,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"有唔同theory<br />\n一 平行世界<br />\n二 根本成個故事係觀世音比悟空發既一場夢 最後先係現實世界"},{"pid":"57ee51d7510bc757b82f5985aa8453dc2bf1bd40","tid":890917,"uid":73935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你當悟空去咗另一個時空，見到一個講野簡結嘅家英哥。<br />\nOr 第一第二頁嘅一切，都係悟空嘅一場夢。<br />\n相似電影<br />\n就好似x-men 未來同盟戰最後嘅狼人見到博士咁，歷史改變咗，所以未來唔同，悟空係唯一一個知道歷史改寫咗嘅人"},{"pid":"1610392d3717f27cf64a3483ee920b450d6a678d","tid":890917,"uid":165202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"睇多幾次就明 然後心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167eaf020bd5726cba80d6b7cb840727d6314cf2","tid":890917,"uid":23734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"悟空 𥄫𥄫"},{"pid":"a533faea6006fc44ac3417700d7d5c9115ccaa83","tid":890917,"uid":97036,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"睇過好多解釋，但呢個我覺得係最好嘅。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n唐三藏是煩膠嗎？<br />\n<br />\n說的是《西遊記之仙履奇緣》中由羅家英扮演的唐三藏。至尊寶（周星馳飾）起初遇上唐三藏，只覺他說話嚕唆，煩膠非常，但最後，他驚訝地發現他這個師父其實是一個言簡意賅之人，而豬八戒（吳盂達飾）也證實了這一點。<br />\n<br />\n觀眾可能認為這不過是搞笑情節，但《哲學有偈傾》的嘉賓陶國璋有一番發人深省的見解。他指出，執迷之人，對世界的一切會感到憤怒、仇恨。孫悟空起初覺得唐三藏說話像烏蠅般嗡嗡叫，代表他未從貪嗔癡中解脫出來，所以就算師父的教誨極其簡潔，唔岩聽就是唔岩聽，怎樣說也覺得很厭煩。一旦緣分來了，覺悟了，心境隨之改變，便看到師父另一個（或本來）的面貌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1056757\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1056757&d=DD0ZIIEfIDfASuvfVMNE3xxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=49619db0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1056757&h=87d49c11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1056757</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁上下意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a72b84be9e763958e09bce8c1a24b8611341b69","tid":890917,"uid":97036,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:09:47.000Z","msg":"所謂 物隨心轉，境由心造<br />\n<br />\n當悟空未看化果陣就覺得師傅好煩<br />\n<br />\n睇透左了，覺悟了，塵世間嘅事唔再留戀了，聽師傅講野自然有另一種感覺"},{"pid":"8e7ede2ad19da6d88be0e149d408feb483c0331f","tid":890917,"uid":82532,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"初頭觀音姐姐都覺佢煩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463e0fbe4298ed1985c13fdfad6925d3843b3f29","tid":890917,"uid":13936,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e7ede2ad19da6d88be0e149d408feb483c0331f","tid":890917,"uid":82532,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"初頭觀音姐姐都覺佢煩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"睇d 人無限解讀就好笑"},{"pid":"b20f311abf8a582599ceea7dc07aad08f97e5d86","tid":890917,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"從前 現在 過去了 再不來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202a4828d16bac958404262884a799299542b4f0","tid":890917,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b20f311abf8a582599ceea7dc07aad08f97e5d86","tid":890917,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"從前 現在 過去了 再不來<img src=